Package com.vmware.vcenter.vm.data_sets

The com.vmware.vcenter.vm.data_sets package provides interfaces for manipulating entries in data sets.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Entries
    The Entries interface provides methods for manipulating individual entries in a data set.
    Entries.DeleteInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Entries#delete vAPI operation.
    Entries.GetInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Entries#get vAPI operation.
    Entries.ListInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Entries#list vAPI operation.
    Entries.SetInvocation
    Invocable that represents the Entries#set vAPI operation.
    EntriesTypes
    The Entries interface provides methods for manipulating individual entries in a data set.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataSetsFactory
    DataSetsFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.vcenter.vm.data_sets package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
    EntriesDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the Entries API service.
    EntriesStub
    Remote stub implementation of the Entries API service.
    StructDefinitions
    Defines the type descriptors for the top-level types in com.vmware.vcenter.vm.data_sets package.
